{"tid":919234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"直布羅陀首席大臣：英脫歐協議將涵蓋此屬地","createTime":"2018-11-28T01:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T01:41:40.000Z","uid":8543,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4002393f272d8afc386c5f2f0d39e32ccd04014d","tid":919234,"uid":8543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T01:41:40.000Z","msg":"（路透馬德里22日電）英國屬地直布羅陀首席大臣（Fabian Picardo）今天表示，英國與歐洲聯盟達成的脫歐協議，將涵蓋與直布羅陀有關的內容。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙要求協議中載明，有關直布羅陀未來地位問題，須由西班牙和英國雙方商定。中央社（翻譯）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9B%B4%E5%B8%83%E7%BE%85%E9%99%80%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3-%E8%8B%B1%E8%84%AB%E6%AD%90%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E5%B0%87%E6%B6%B5%E8%93%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%B1%AC%E5%9C%B0-150527966.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%259B%25B4%25E5%25B8%2583%25E7%25BE%2585%25E9%2599%2580%25E9%25A6%2596%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2587%25A3-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E8%2584%25AB%25E6%25AD%2590%25E5%258D%2594%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%25B6%25B5%25E8%2593%258B%25E6%25AD%25A4%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0-150527966.html&d=E1T%2B3%2Fwi7mooJkZ6DPK9TdibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=0abee5fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%9B%B4%E5%B8%83%E7%BE%85%E9%99%80%E9%A6%96%E5%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E8%87%A3-%E8%8B%B1%E8%84%AB%E6%AD%90%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0%E5%B0%87%E6%B6%B5%E8%93%8B%E6%AD%A4%E5%B1%AC%E5%9C%B0-150527966.html</a>"}]}